title: Beautiful Lilydale Area , Spacious 1 BR. Great Floor Plan!!
posting_body: ['Here at The Riverwood we offer some great amenities for you to enjoy.', 'Heated parking, in unit washer and dryer, outdoor pool and fire pit!', 'We have it all for you to enjoy and to complement your lifestyle!', '***Please note, pricing is subject to change daily.', 'Adjusting your move-in date or lease term will adjust pricing.', 'Payment of the application fee will lock the rental rate for only the selected lease term and move-in date.', "Do not forget to mention that you heard about our community through Craig's List to get a special $150.00 rent referral credit!", '***', 'We have 133 apartments with 14 different floor plans!', 'All our apartments are non-furnished.', 'The monthly rent for our apartments ranges generally depends on your desired move-in date, and how long you desire to lease the apartment.', 'We have lease terms available from three (3) to thirteen (13) months.', 'Which offers great flexibility for you!', 'One indoor parking is included in rent and ample outdoor parking is available!', 'We are a Smoke--Free Community!', 'Our Security deposit is generally $500-$1000 and an application fee of $50 per applicant with a one time admin fee of $150.', 'We allow birds, fish & cats & dogs.', 'Take a look at our website The Riverwood: <URL>', 'I look forward to finding your new apartment home!', 'The Riverwood', '1015 Sibley Memorial Hwy | Lilydale, MN 55118', '<URL>', '| Bigos Management', 'do NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers', 'do NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers']
